    "title": "Such a Cod Finger.",
    "description": "Fires a single bullet that spawns additional pellets over time in flight, up to 13 extra (14 total). Extra pellets appear at roughly 30 ms intervals in a fixed pattern: +1 five times, then +2 twice, then +4 at the end. Increased zoom. Reduced damage and fire rate. Damage scales with travel time, reaching up to 14x at maximum split."
